name: public-land-survey-system-of-louisiana-geographic-nad83-usgs-2003-plss-la-usgs-2003
notes: This data set portrays the Public Land Surveys of the United States, including areas of private survey, Donation Land Claims, and Land Grants and Civil Colonies. This is a revised version of the May, 2002 data set.
